title: The Beatles - Revolver Sessions 4
description:
The Beatles
Revolver Sessions 4
cd or dvd (Revolver, Anthology, Yellow Sub Songtrack)> eac > extractions, edits etc > flac

This set is mostly outfakes taken from the various cds, organized and edited to show the sequence of the recording of the Revolver album. This final disc is mostly comprised of mono and stereo mixes. Mono source: Another Phase except for Eleanor Rigby which is from the 3" cd single. Stereo source: Millenium Remaster Blue Box
